{"tid":1920519,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許留山遭入稟申請清盤　排期6月3日審","createTime":"2020-03-11T13:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T13:33:36.000Z","uid":40152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"983cdab19571f3e2b8304d8b68adcb0e66502b29","tid":1920519,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200311/s00001/dbf824dd9ff021788d336055bc670e9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200311%2Fs00001%2Fdbf824dd9ff021788d336055bc670e9a.jpg&h=6ee6322d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被多名業主追討舖租的甜品品牌「許留山」，今日（11日）遭權記玩具有限公司入稟高等法院申請清盤。司法機構網頁顯示，案件已排期6月3日處理。<br />\n<br />\n許留山今年1月回覆本報查詢時指出，過去數月已關閉10餘間門店，主要集中在旅遊區和個別住宅區，形容公司業務去年受反修例運動巨大衝擊，來港遊客急劇減少，導致其傳統旅遊區門店業務減少六至七成。<br />\n<br />\n除被清盤申請，許留山位於藍田匯景廣場的分店再遭業主Bansque Limited入稟高等法院，要求收回舖位，以及追討分店去年10月開始拖欠、逾19萬元的租金。翻查報道，Bansque Limited去年11月已入稟高院，向許留山追討7至10月的租金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200311/s00001/1583922523548/%E8%A8%B1%E7%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4-%E6%8E%92%E6%9C%9F6%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E5%AF%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200311%2Fs00001%2F1583922523548%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259B%25A4-%25E6%258E%2592%25E6%259C%259F6%25E6%259C%25883%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AF%25A9&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stlMsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=5026e512\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200311%2Fs00001%2F1583922523548%2F%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259B%25A4-%25E6%258E%2592%25E6%2